data.description: Welcome to this must-see in The Landings at New Riverside! This stunning 4BD/2.5BA home offers privacy and tranquility with the large front porch, fenced-in backyard, patio, and serene wooded views. Inside, enjoy the fantastic eat-in kitchen with a large pantry and open-concept living room. The private office is the perfect quiet retreat. First-floor primary suite is complete with large closets and an en-suite bath, while the remaining guest bedrooms and bonus loft upstairs offer versatility for friends and family. Don't miss the chance to visit this exceptional home!
